Popups

Show popups when visiting, exiting or reading page

Main Features:

  • Popup When Visiting Page
  • Time Based Popup
  • Popup Then Scrolled to Bottom
  • Popup on Exit Intent

Popup When Visiting Page

Show popup to visitors when they visit the specific page or any page (use * for any page). Show once or each time they visit this page.

Time Based Popup

Show popup to visitors when they spent specified time on the specific pageor any page (use * for any page). Show once or each time they visit this page.

Popup Then Scrolled to Bottom

Show popup to visitors when they scroll to the very bottom of the specific pageor any page (use * for any page). Show once or each time they visit this page.

Popup on Exit Intent

Show popup when visitors are intending to exit your website from specific pageor any page (use * for any page). Can be shown once or each time a visitor tries to exit.
